someone or something, huh?

253
00:13:45,700 --> 00:13:46,400
Yeah.

254
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:48,400
Looks like he may have
fought back after all.

255
00:13:48,500 --> 00:13:51,100
Maybe. Keep me posted.

256
