00:28:44,700 --> 00:28:47,200
His kidneys failed, didn't they?

519
00:28:50,800 --> 00:28:53,300
Uli wod have given him both of mine,

520
00:28:53,300 --> 00:28:56,800
but I wasn't a match, and there
